OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Journalists across Ecuador have been   
OL,6, targeted by explosive devices sent     
OL,7, through the post.                      
OL,9,FOne presenter, Lenin Artieda, was      
OL,10,Finjured when he opened the envelope in 
OL,11,Fthe middle of the newsroom.            
OL,13,FHe said the explosive device looked    
OL,14,Flike a USB drive. He plugged it into   
OL,15,Fhis computer and it detonated.         
OL,17,FThe Ecuadorean attorney-general's      
OL,18,Fdepartment confirmed it had opened a   
OL,19,Fterrorism investigation into the       
OL,20,Fletters on Monday.                     
